{"tid":1046661,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[球王, 難以置信] GIF - C.朗1球將對手玩弄於鼓掌間！","createTime":"2019-03-04T11:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T07:55:07.000Z","uid":34571,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fdacf88b27e7a0d3502780f2b84e373deec6ce","tid":1046661,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/03/04/f/fa6811250388de4d0e2e1afe469b51a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2Ff%2Ffa6811250388de4d0e2e1afe469b51a5.jpg&h=72194f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這也太秀了吧</div><br />\n<br />\n對陣拿玻里，C.朗拿度雖然沒有取得入球，但他的表現仍然十分亮眼，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一次秀翻全場的操作</span>，更是讓人們見識到了這位巨星的出眾技術。<br />\n<br />\n  在祖記對陣拿玻里的比賽中，當C.朗拿度製造紅牌、幫助球隊取得11打10的優勢時，祖雲達斯卻沒能拿出具有統治力的表現，反而被拿玻里頻頻反擊、快攻。關鍵時刻，C.朗拿度在前場發揮出了重要的作用。<br />\n<br />\n  在一次進攻中，C.朗拿度接到隊友的長傳，卻無法順利轉身。在這個看似「死局」的情況下，C.朗拿度卻出人意料地用胸部將球彈起，然後不等皮球落地，直接用大腿連顛了3下球，<span style=\"color: red;\">將拿玻里上搶合圍的球員玩弄於股掌之間</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  眼看對手即將完成「關門防守」，C.朗拿度也適時地將球挑傳給上來接應的文素基治，最終這次看似即將流產的進攻，也轉化成了另一次有威脅的角球，而這次角球，最終轉化成了詹的入球。<br />\n<br />\n  以往，人們總是指摘C.朗拿度「只會射門」，而忽略了<span style=\"color: red;\">他出色的腳下技術和出眾的想像力</span>。這一次，C.朗拿度用自己的表現告訴全世界：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誰還不是個能秀翻全場的魔術手呢。</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc2f537ac03adfe5a01d24d4baf068374c3aaa70","tid":1046661,"uid":65743,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/195706_2ce8e3ee4dd2baf74772d19f5eb92e02.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F195706_2ce8e3ee4dd2baf74772d19f5eb92e02.gif&h=7a772a66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e5af01bc9fed4c4ccf015a995af7a228535e6bd","tid":1046661,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"Siuma都做到"},{"pid":"6d312f15997588efbce8c996e163a2ffafb3cc58","tid":1046661,"uid":38543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"666"},{"pid":"16afb8c233604bd3671e3e7ef5ba614871c95bf8","tid":1046661,"uid":149607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"真係360度無死角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2572b0c9b1f7c1e84bc38813eff640566c7aa1ad","tid":1046661,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4be68bbfc1870b30664d39323214d2c02f5d8e","tid":1046661,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dff9ea80c7758a1a50315b263beadaf562a50ce","tid":1046661,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"見過陳七對菲律賓仔都做過"},{"pid":"bf6066787cdd1de0622fc4bd98bf2ac41444bfb8","tid":1046661,"uid":14652,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"唔質疑C朗既能力<br />\n但係咁樣都好可以打成篇文真係太誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41283dd89d7d9c0bce9d28d0de942bb8b3774ca","tid":1046661,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b206484416b9f7e53dd0ae281821cbfb97bee601","tid":1046661,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"香港學界都有 李三腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif